name: Storyboard-auto-x-mobility
label: The 4G Mobility - Overview and Insights

widgets.title: Top 5 Lowest IMS Gx CCR-U Success Rate
widgets.extra_filter: IMSA_Credit_control_Update_Success_Rate >= 90 and schema is 'imsa' and servname is 'Gx'

widgets.title: Top 5 Lowest IMS Gx CCR-I Success Rate

widgets.title: Top 5 Lowest IMS Gx RAR Success Rate
widgets.extra_filter: Gx_RAR_Success_Rate >= 90  and schema is 'imsa' and servname is 'Gx'

widgets.title: By State
widgets.extra_filter: i_state does not contains 'cancelled' AND network_type in ['FirstNet','Consumer','Enterprise']

widgets.title: By State

widgets.title: By Network

widgets.title: FirstNet

widgets.title: Consumer

widgets.title: Enterprise
